            "description": "Update space fields (partial update / patch semantics).\n\nAuth: BrandManager ✅, StoreManager (own store) ✅ (SystemAdmin ❌)\n\nNotes:\n- Only send fields you want to change. Omitted/null fields keep their current value.\n- storeId in body is always ignored (cannot move a space to a different store).\n- Name uniqueness is checked only if name actually changes (self-collision excluded)."
